- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is relevant as the paper proposes algorithms for network inference. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possibility as the paper deals with understanding which properties can be predicted with available resources. 
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is also a possibility as the paper proves an information-theoretic lower bound on the number of traces required for optimal inference.
